description: Demolition of the Magistrates Court and redevelopment to provide a building comprising of two basements, ground and part eight/part nine upper floors to Horseferry Road frontage and stepping down to part five/part seven upper floors to Romney Street frontage, with central courtyard, balconies and terraces to provide 144 residential units (7x studios, 34x1 bed, 57x2 bed and 46x3 bed); 130 car parking spaces at basement level in automated car park accessed from Romney Street and 190 cycle spaces.
